<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Blood Order Request Approved</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.5;
        color: #222222;
      }

      a {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.25;
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        margin-top: 0;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .divider {
        border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }

      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 700px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .email-header {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 30px;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .email-body {
        padding: 14px;
        background-color: #f4f3f3;
      }

      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1e1e1e;
        padding: 14px;
        color: #ef5b5b;
      }

      img {
        padding: 24px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1720958373/logo1_ewwjxg.png"
          height="100px"
          width="400px"
          alt="BloodBridge Logo"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <h1>Blood Order Request Approved</h1>
        <p>Hello <%= name %>,</p>
        <p>Your blood order request has been approved. Here are the details of your order:</p>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p><strong>Blood Type:</strong> <%= bloodType %></p>
        <p><strong>Units Required:</strong> <%= units %></p>
        <p><strong>Urgency Level:</strong> <%= urgency %></p>
        <p><strong>Rate per Unit:</strong> Rs. <%= ratePerUnit %></p>
        <p><strong>Total Cost:</strong> Rs. <%= totalCost %></p>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <p>Please visit our center with this email confirmation to collect your blood order.</p>
        <p><strong>Collection Center Details:</strong></p>
        <p>Location: Blood Bank Center</p>
        <p>Address: 123 Main Street, Cityville</p>
        <p>Operating Hours: 9:00 AM - 5:00 PM</p>
        <p>Contact: (123) 456-7890</p>
        
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dap91fhxh/image/upload/v1720957791/hero1_trpojy.jpg"
          alt="Blood Donation"
          height="250px"
          width="500px"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>
          If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to contact us at
          <a href="mailto:support@bloodbridge.com">support@bloodbridge.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>